							</a> <div class="show-mob overview-mob container"> <h2>Radisson Blu Hotel, Cairo Heliopolis</h2> <div class="__text js-text-overview"> <p><p>Radisson Blu Hotel, Cairo Heliopolis is a charming 5-star venue set 4.3 km from Baron Palace and 4.6 km from Saqqara Sakkara Pyramids. This exclusive accommodation, built in 2009, is decorated in an Egyptian style.</p></p> <p><p>This property is set next to Arab Academy for Science, Technology & Maritime Transport and in the centre of Cairo. These comfortable rooms overlook the lagoon.</p><p> You will find a stadium and golf courses in the vicinity.</p></p> <p><p> Non-smoking units are equipped with free wireless internet, a kitchen area and iHome. There are private bathrooms with a roll in shower, a rainfall shower and bath sheets along with an electric kettle, a dishwasher and coffee and tea making facilities for self-catering.</p></p> <p><p> Wake up with a wonderful buffet breakfast served in the restaurant. Indulge in Italian delicacies at Mix  restaurant. In the lobby bar you can find the refreshing drinks. You can try Asian cuisine in a coffee shop which is located very close by.</p><p>Radisson Blu Hotel, Cairo Heliopolis is at a short distance from El Giza train station.</p><p> Guests can make use of a health club, a spa area and a whirlpool tub along with steam baths, Turkish bath and massage. Radisson Blu Hotel, Cairo Heliopolis also offers fitness classes and a gym.</p></p> </div> <div class="js-btn-description"> <a class="js-more">+ More</a> <a class="js-hide" style="display: none">- Hide</a> </div> </div> <div class="availability-deck js-availbox-cont js-avail-scroll-point " id="availability-form"> <div class="reserv-title"> <span class="is-main-form">Online Reservation</span> <span class="is-for-popup">Enter your dates to see prices</span> </div> <form autocomplete="off" class="js-avail-form" action="#rooms" method="get" formtarget="#rooms"> <fieldset class="form-fieldset js-calendar-cont"> <span class="form